- Use the App Router for better performance and organization of routes.
- Implement proper error boundaries to handle errors gracefully.
- Utilize built-in image optimization features for faster load times.
- Leverage static site generation (SSG) and server-side rendering (SSR) appropriately based on content needs.
- Optimize API routes for performance and security.